lead_paragraph: Struggling Hamburg SV have appointed Markus Gisdol as their new coach, hours after sacking Bruno Labbadia in the wake of a fourth straight Bundesliga defeat.

headline.print_headline: Coach Gisdol Replaces Labbadia at Strugglers Hamburg
headline.main: Coach Gisdol Replaces Labbadia at Strugglers Hamburg
